quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,"“Ndipo pamene atumiki athu adamdzera Ibrahim ndi nkhani yabwino (yoti abereka Mneneri Ishaq), adanenanso: “Ndithu tiwaononga eni mudzi uwu (wa Sodom); ndithu iwowo ngochimwa.”"
  29,32,"“(Mneneri Ibrahim) adati: “Koma mmenemo muli Luti.” Iwo adati: “Ife ndife odziwa kwambiri za omwe ali m’menemo; ndithu timpulumutsa iye ndi banja lake kupatula mkazi wake; iye ndi mmodzi wa otsalira (woonongeka).”"
  29,33,"“Ndipo pamene atumiki athu adamdzera Luti, adawadandaulira ndi kuwadera nkhawa; (ndipo iwo) adati: “Usaope ndipo usadandaule. Ndithu ife tikupulumutsa ndi banja lako kupatula mkazi wako; iye ndi mmodzi wa otsalira (woonongeka).”"
  29,34,““Ndithu ife tiwatsitsira chilango choipa kuchokera kumwamba eni mudzi uwu chifukwa cha kuchimwa kwawo (ndi kuukira malamulo a Allah).”
  29,35,“Ndipo ndithu tidasiya chizindikiro mmenemo choonekera kwa anthu anzeru
  29,36,"“Ndipo ku Madiyan (tidatumako) m’bale wawo Shuaib, ndipo adati: “E inu anthu anga! Mpembedzeni Allah ndipo opani tsiku lachimaliziro musanke mu ononga pa dziko.”"
  29,37,"“Koma adamutsutsa. Ndipo kugwedezeka kwa nthaka kudawachotsa moyo wawo, ndipo kudawachera ali gwadegwade m’nyumba zawo (atafa)"
  29,38,"“Nawonso Âdi ndi Asamudu (tidawaononga). Ndipo mokhala mwawo mukudziwika kwa inu. Ndipo satana adawakometsera zochita zawo (zoipa), ndipo adawatsekereza ku njira (zabwino) chikhalirecho adali openya (anzeru zawo)"